<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<title>Ʋba Chihowa chia ma! ƲIT94</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba Chihowa chia ma!
 Himak okhlili ka,
 Pit chi aiokpahanchi hosh,
 E chieya hoke.

[V2]
 Ish pi apesahanchi na,
 Pi okcha̱ya hocha,
 Pit e chi anukfihinlit,
 E taloho̱wʋshke.

[V3]
 Chihowa Chitokaka ma!
 Pi̱ki chia hokʋt,
 Chiso ilbʋsha pia ka
 Ish pi̱ nukha̱klashke.

[V4]
 Nana il aiashʋcheka
 Mominchi fehna hosh
 Isht ish pi̱ kanchi pulla cha,
 Chimmi ish pikbashke.

[V5]
 Himak ninak fehna hoka
 Ish pi̱ bilinchi na,
 Achukma pi nuhu̱si na
 Oho̱nna pullashke.

[V6]
 Nana ik achukmo hokʋt
 Pim ʋla yobakma,
 Ish pi̱ kanʋllihinchi na,
 Pi achukma̱kashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Evening Song.</aka>
</song>